            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>I am on the point of departure but catch a moment to say that I have left at <persName ref="pe0327">Robson</persName>
                    eleven drawings, nine of which are single &amp; two double, their cost 3 â€“ 5. 0 &amp; I think not dear. they &amp;
                    the book<note type="editorial">Neither the drawings nor the book mentioned have been identified.</note> <persName ref="pe0327">Robson</persName> says that it
                    <add place="above">shall</add> be instantly sent. any Commands you may have in <placeName ref="pl0731">Wales</placeName>
                    shall with pleasure be obeyed. best wishes &amp; Complim<hi rend="superscript">ts</hi> attend the Ladies.<note type="editorial"><persName ref="pe0331">Elizabeth</persName> and <persName ref="pe0336">Catherine Bull</persName>, and, possibly, <persName ref="pe0346">Levinia Luther</persName>.</note>
                    You may inclose your answer to our friend <persName ref="pe0284">Th. Hunt</persName> <placeName ref="pl1095">S. Audley street</placeName>.
                    till <persName ref="pe0015">our member</persName> returns.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>with compliments &amp; best wishes to <persName ref="pe0331 pe0336 pe0346">the Ladies</persName>
                    <lb/>I rest D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir
                    <lb/>most faithfully y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed>
                    <dateline><placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> <del>ma</del>April 8<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. 1785</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><stamp type="postmark">8 AP</stamp> <stamp type="frank"><placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> April Eighth 1785; <persName ref="pe0284">Th<gap unit="letters" quantity="2" reason="illegible"/> Hunt</persName>;<note type="editorial">This material is handwritten.</note> FRE<gap unit="letters" quantity="1" reason="illegible"/></stamp></p>
                <p><address>
                    <addrLine><persName ref="pe0313">Rich<hi rend="superscript">d</hi> Bull, Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></persName> | <placeName ref="pl1013">Northcote Hall | Isle of Wight | Hampshire</placeName></addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
